# Regression-Benchmark — WHITELIST.
# Ignore everything, then re-include only the curated deliverables. This
# guarantees no log, virtualenv, Django git mirror, downloaded dataset, Docker
# artefact, or any large file (>1 MB) can ever be tracked — only the files
# explicitly un-ignored below are committable.

# Ignore all top-level entries...
/*
# ...but keep these:
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/kt_bucket.py

# patches/ — only the mirror patch
!/patches
/patches/*
!/patches/swebench-git-mirror.patch

# results/ — only the two curated result reports
!/results
/results/*
!/results/random_sample_25_django.json
!/results/biased_17_unresolved-weighted_django.json
